 4. Conditions of Distribution.

 4.1 License Text Requirement.

 You must include a copy of this License with any copy of the Work,
 Contributions, or Derivative Works that You Distribute, in the form of
 a LICENSE file, documentation, or other reasonable and accessible
 location.

 4.2 Preservation of Notices.

 You must retain, in the Work and in any Derivative Works that You
 Distribute, all copyright notices, license notices, and attribution
 notices that are present in the Work, except where removal is required
 by law.

 4.3 No Lockdown of the Licensed Work.

 When You Distribute the Work or Derivative Works, You may not impose
 legal, contractual, or technological measures that prevent recipients
 from exercising the rights granted to them under this License with
 respect to the Work or Derivative Works.

 This section does not restrict agreements or measures that are unrelated
 to the exercise of rights in the Work itself.

 4.4 Hardware and Physical Works.

 Where the Work includes design files for hardware or physical objects,
 this License grants rights only to the extent that applicable law
 recognizes copyright or related rights in such design files.

 This License grants no rights in patents except as expressly granted in
 Section 3.

